data.description: This jewel box garden home just moments from darling Downtown Tucker is too good to be true. Perfectly situated inside a well-kept neighborhood, you'll never want to leave unless you're dining out on the town or shopping at the new Publix nearby! This completely stepless house has been lovingly cared for and updated, and features new premium wood tiled flooring throughout, a new garage door, fresh exterior paint, newer water heater, 2-year-old roof and more! At the front of the house, the sunny eat-in kitchen with its original charm opens to the private brick enclosed front patio.  An oversized bonus room with windows on two sides doubles as a third bedroom, with a laundry room closet and gorgeous, updated half bath. A spacious fireside living room opens to another private patio space that leads to a fenced-in, low maintenance yard. Two oversized bedrooms with walk-in closets and ensuite bathrooms are perfectly placed in the back of the house. The primary closet features a fantastic custom closet design and the primary bathroom was upgraded to the hilt with spa-like features. Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own an amazing home with easy access to all the nearby amenities of downtown Tucker - and more!
